{"tid":2029094,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美卿：低估中共敵視自由國家程度","createTime":"2020-05-22T05:43:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T06:03:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"587a4ebbb00428dad661683043368a67c1eafb09","tid":2029094,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:43:03.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200522/2PQYUGSEPQBAVM3ZSHBEVUBHHA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200522%2F2PQYUGSEPQBAVM3ZSHBEVUBHHA%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSl3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=6f2c523e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200522%2F2PQYUGSEPQBAVM3ZSHBEVUBHHA%2F&h=1b042a1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200522/2PQYUGSEPQBAVM3ZSHBEVUBHHA/</a><br />\n<br />\n美卿：低估中共敵視自由國家程度<br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧指，美國數十年來以為中國會越來越自由民主但事與願違，又批評中國承諾捐20億美元（156億港元）對抗武漢肺炎疫情是微不足道。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：英媒分析：美疫情亂局助習脫困<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200522/large/1590074731_08df.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200522%2Flarge%2F1590074731_08df.gif&h=20eb295e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱習應任記者提問證無瞞疫<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧前日稱傳媒聚焦疫情危機，卻看不到中共為世界帶來的挑戰，「自1949年以來，中國一直被一個殘暴獨裁政權和共產政權統治。幾十年來我們以為透過貿易、科學交流和外交接觸。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧又不認同中國國家主席習近平聲稱中國一直透明處理疫情，批評北京繼續扣起病毒樣本，並拒絕讓外人進入設施調查等。他揚言若習近平想證明中國具透明度，應開記者會任記者隨意提問。他又期望北京履行20億美元捐。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人趙立堅批評蓬佩奧信口雌黃極不負責，質疑美國為何1至3月無採取有力舉措防控又反對戴口罩。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/路透社"},{"pid":"d977bd4e057096d4c982492b3062f332d940b422","tid":2029094,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:43:35.000Z","msg":"［Twitter國安法]各國議員連珠炮發，誓要以實際行動保衛香港！抵抗邪惡中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2028898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2028898</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ef3c7e275cabbfa038be7258920f936ebd2e65dc","tid":2029094,"uid":246968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:47:19.000Z","msg":"因為世衛反對封關，反對發出指引全民戴口罩，而中共喺世衛背後做左啲乜心知肚明"},{"pid":"40c5ef7e2ffb410a95378e31cdcbbac2097c4c4b","tid":2029094,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:48:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9dd1168b0ab750b3300d4d614b060654ac3837","tid":2029094,"uid":259402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"世衛有叫人帶口罩咩當初<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645a1927f2834449ad85f63de9aa838cb722164a","tid":2029094,"uid":24924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:55:15.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"e202385045407722e8ac32d19d409f51da4c6c88","tid":2029094,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:55:18.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"156d20ed3ef77bd42132b81f9e2bf3e6758394ed","tid":2029094,"uid":83623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb9dd1168b0ab750b3300d4d614b060654ac3837","tid":2029094,"uid":259402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:49:05.000Z","msg":"世衛有叫人帶口罩咩當初<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T06:03:36.000Z","msg":"Day1到現在都叫你唔好帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}